493
00:21:39,080 --> 00:21:41,720
( Koichi screams )

494
00:21:44,090 --> 00:21:46,020
♪

495
00:22:06,680 --> 00:22:08,140
♪ Anytime I need
to see your face ♪

496
00:22:08,180 --> 00:22:10,880
♪ I just close my eyes,
and I am taken to a place ♪

497
00:22:10,910 --> 00:22:12,850
♪ where your crystal mind
and magenta feelings ♪

498
00:22:12,880 --> 00:22:14,750
♪ take up shelter
